LowerLeftCorner: The lower left corner of the box.
UpperRightCorner: The upper right corner of the box.
bAbsolute: If true, the box coordinates are in world space./
bKillInside:
If true, particles INSIDE the box will be killed.
If false (the default), particles OUTSIDE the box will be killed.
bAxisAlignedAndFixedSize: If true, the box will always be axis aligned and non-scalable.
